feature_description: In most cases, concessive semantics ("Although X, Y") is expressed by a combination of a conditional converb and an additive particle. However, some dialects allow for other constuctions as well --- to convey concessive meaning, additive may attach to non-conditional verbforms. Parataxis (i.e. juxtaposition of two finite clauses) is also a frequent strategy to express this semantics.

feature_description: Non-specific indefinite pronouns are derived from WH-pronouns (known to speaker, unknown to hearer). There is variation across the dialect as to (1) which suffixes are attached to WH-pronouns and (2) whether those suffixes attach to WH-pronouns directly or a copula occurs between them. In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde).
stimuli: 2. К тебе всегда кто-нибудь приходит.
expected: 2. zaχda hammiše wɨšijde ruʔur
name: айдемир

In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde).
stimuli: 1. К тебе кто-то приходил.
expected: 1. zaχdɨ wišijde jirqɨraj
name: нархамнум

feature_description: Non-specific indefinite pronouns are derived from WH-pronouns (known to speaker, unknown to hearer). There is variation across the dialect as to (1) which suffixes are attached to WH-pronouns and (2) whether those suffixes attach to WH-pronouns directly or a copula occurs between them. In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde).
stimuli: Фатима что-то приготовила [но не знаю, что].
answer: fatima šuwki ide iled haq’ɨ i
name: асхад

feature_description: Non-specific indefinite pronouns are derived from WH-pronouns (known to speaker, unknown to hearer). There is variation across the dialect as to (1) which suffixes are attached to WH-pronouns and (2) whether those suffixes attach to WH-pronouns directly or a copula occurs between them. In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde).
stimuli: 1. К тебе кто-то приходил.
expected: 1. zaχdɨ wišijde jirqɨraj
name: жанна
schooling: до 3 класса в куфа, потом рутул до 7 класса
residence_place: балашиха, в куфа летом в гости

There is variation across the dialect as to (1) which suffixes are attached to WH-pronouns and (2) whether those suffixes attach to WH-pronouns directly or a copula occurs between them. In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde).
stimuli: 2. К тебе всегда кто-нибудь приходит.
expected: 2. zaχda hammiše wɨšijde ruʔur
name: Расим

feature_description: The construction for the expression of free-choice indefinite semantics ("whatever, whoever"). Similarly to non-specific indefinite pronouns, they are derived from WH-pronouns. There is variation across the dialect as to (1) which suffixes are attached to WH-pronouns and (2) whether those suffixes attach to WH-pronouns directly or a copula occurs between them. In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde). In some cases a periphrastic construction is employed --- with some form of the verb "want" ("do a wanted thing" instead of "do whatever").
stimuli: Расул съест что угодно (он голодный).
expected: rasulɨ šuwgɨxɨ ilesɨ.
name: айдемир

In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde). In some cases a periphrastic construction is employed --- with some form of the verb "want" ("do a wanted thing" instead of "do whatever").
stimuli: Кто угодно может эту работу сделать.
answer: sienbišda wikes waʔas hemi gʷalaχ / wɨšgajde — НЕТ
name: тажир
long_periods_outside: учился в дербенте, работал в бабаюртовском районе. но с 86 года тут

feature_description: The construction for the expression of free-choice indefinite semantics ("whatever, whoever"). Similarly to non-specific indefinite pronouns, they are derived from WH-pronouns. There is variation across the dialect as to (1) which suffixes are attached to WH-pronouns and (2) whether those suffixes attach to WH-pronouns directly or a copula occurs between them. In some cases, non-specific pronouns require an additive particles. The order of those elements --- WH-(COP)-INDEF-ADD is also subject to variation. Note that, in many cases, the suffix deriving non-specific pronouns is identical with the suffix for counterfactual conditionals (e.g., de/jde). In some cases a periphrastic construction is employed --- with some form of the verb "want" ("do a wanted thing" instead of "do whatever").
stimuli: Я пойду с тобой куда угодно.
answer: zɨ rurusɨ waqʷan hilegadexa / zɨ rurusɨ waqʷan hilegade — «я пойду с тобой куда-то», но неизвестно куда / zɨ rurusɨ waqʷan hile hɨgadexa — я пойду с тобой куда тебе захочется, но кажется не ок
name: nazile
